OL,5, In the darkest corner of a grand museum
OL,6, that looks like a neo-classical palace 
OL,7, lies a not-so-secret room.             
OL,9,FIt is filled with statues of Congolese 
OL,10,Fpeople, which have been regarded as    
OL,11,Fracist, that were once part of the     
OL,12,Fpermanent exhibition.                  
OL,14,FSchoolchildren on educational tours    
OL,15,Ffile past the Leopard Man, men with    
OL,16,Fspears and women almost naked.         
OL,18,FThis is the Africa Museum in Tervuren, 
OL,19,Fjust outside Brussels, and until       
OL,20,Frecently those sculptures were part of 
OL,21,Fthe permanent exhibition.              
